snippet.title: What's New in the Hello Neighbor VR Game? First Gameplay Trailer!
snippet.description:
One step closer to entering Mr. Peterson’s House (literally)🏡Hello Neighbor: Search and Rescue VR is now available for pre-order on Oculus Store!

Pre-order to be the first to confront your fears and attempt to free your friend👇
https://tblink.co/HNVROculus

Join the Neighborhood: http://discord.gg/neighborgames

Be in the Know at https://www.helloneighborvr.com/

Follow us on social media:
Twitter: https://twitter.com/NeighborGamesHQ
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/NeighborGamesHQ
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/NeighborGamesHQ
